{"tid":1373873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Online自衛隊] 免被狗衝，堅守不攻 組織防犬公會","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T19:43:25.000Z","uid":102587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75f06bc3acad56268624a48784b80080cdbc6607","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"致每一個玩香城Online的香港人:<br />\n<br />\n自 7.14沙田 / 7.21上環/元朗 / 7.27元朗<br />\n<br />\n每次被狗黑推進，清場，<br />\n全部狗入夜後，都喪盡天良，<br />\n最後都用過份武力，連記者都打，女人都禽。<br />\n唔想再見倒以下情況發生<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MwnuV65.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMwnuV65.gif&h=a80bc05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日，小弟有提議，望巴絲打遂一評價<br />\n<br />\n1. 自組自衛隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以TG 組織自衛隊只守不攻，為數10人一隊。</span><br />\n簡單防守裝備，Helmet ，Hiking stick<br />\n招募非前線玩家，如有未決心者，不如玩家建立安全區，比前線一個安心之所。<br />\n<br />\n2. 堅守每個地鐵站出入口<br />\n每當警察推進，推至夜晚，警方厲必提升武力，(出速狗小隊/Gas)<br />\n當玩家陣形衝散，就遂一追捕，繼而狂摳。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自衛小隊必須堅守每一個地鐵站出口，提供一個安全區域，比撤離的玩家。<br />\n若果狗稍有推進至地鐵站口，定必自衛反擊，保護撤離人士，<br />\n如遭遠程進攻，退入地鐵站內。 以防今日人士散去時被狗追擊。</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 每個地鐵出口，可互補人數，一方有難，八方支援<br />\n每組十人，當一方有事，短途程可互補不足<br />\n<br />\n4.防守時間<br />\n每次運動的7點左右，當玩家散去，狗仍然都會推進咬鳩玩家，<br />\n我地最終目標: 保護玩家，以防比狗突擊<br />\nPS.搵唔倒今日元運打狗張gif<br />\n<br />\n所有部署，適用任個進入室內的門口！"},{"pid":"60e2ff01abfe44c87a3782cf85fe0cc341b2466b","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ab4fafbe53ac6488f42f47f373d1e8b506446c","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60e2ff01abfe44c87a3782cf85fe0cc341b2466b","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"810348b580731802f4e05370caf2a3351307cc8c","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ab4fafbe53ac6488f42f47f373d1e8b506446c","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60e2ff01abfe44c87a3782cf85fe0cc341b2466b","tid":1373873,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T19:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}